      • delta

        final com.google.common.base.Optional<org.eclipse.core.resources.IResourceDelta> delta
        Currently visited resource delta, not necessarily the one returned by event.getDelta() since it may also another deeper in the delta tree.

        Note that if resource delta is set, then resource is not set. To obtain current resource corresponding to this delta use delta.getResource().

      • resource

        final com.google.common.base.Optional<org.eclipse.core.resources.IResource> resource

        Note that if resource is set, then resource delta is not set.
